Title: node collector: add priorityClassName, nodeSelector and tolerations
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: helm
Date: 1650897464
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 1.0.0-beta.2

The helm chart now supports the following additional settings available for the
node collector: priorityClassName, nodeSelector, and tolerations. These
settings are optional and help ensure that node collectors run on each node.
